    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >There's a big alien mess and somebody's gotta clean it up...</h2>Control an alien infested space station from the safety of your security desk in this funny, brain bending VR simulator game. You're a space security guard; you need to guide the station janitor, Lenny, through dangerous situations while earning achievements along the way.<br><br><br><strong>Use every tool at your disposal:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Control the space facility from the comfort of your security desk<br></li><li> Scour video feeds for alien movements and secrets<br></li><li> Pilot security drones to explore, distract aliens and lead Lenny to safety<br></li><li> Traverse the facility unreliable minimap<br></li><li> Deal with the station's faulty software systems<br></li><li> Enjoy sweet tunes from your office radio</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768730/extras/be7a4da13b52d21a2a11d2da4bfdea95.avif?t=1648453877\" width=616 height=250 /></span>",
